## 4. Reporting & Analytics (Dashboard)

**Supporting Domain — Query/Read Model (CQRS read side)** Read-only projections over synced Submission data, powering the Admin Dashboard and the anonymised Public Dashboard. Deliberately has no aggregates of its own — it is a query/reporting layer over the Field Data Collection context's data, decoupled so exports and chart queries never mutate write-side state.

**Read Models (query side, no aggregates):**

- SubmissionSummary — total counts by form type / district / gender / FY period
- DistrictAggregate — per-district roll-up used for bar charts & heat map
- DataCollectorLeaderboardEntry — collector, cumulative count, breakdown by form type/district/period (DASH-07)
- TimeSeriesPoint — submissions-over-time series for line graphs
- PendingSyncSnapshot — PENDING/SYNCED/FLAGGED counts per collector/device (DASH-08)
- PublicAnonymisedRecord — a Submission projection with all PII (name, phone, collector identity) stripped, used exclusively by Public Dashboard queries and exports

**Domain Services:**

- ExportGenerator — produces CSV/Excel/PDF from a read-model query result
- AnonymisationProjector — strips PII when building PublicAnonymisedRecord

