## 3.2 Class Responsibilities by Package

**domain.user**

| **Class(es)** | **Responsibility** |
|---------------|-------------------|
| User | Aggregate root. Enforces phone-number identity, role, active status; factory methods createByAdmin(...), deactivate(), reactivate(), resetPassword(). |
| Role, AccountStatus, PhoneNumber, PasswordHash | Value objects — immutable, self-validating. |
| ManageUserAccountsUseCase (in port) | createDataCollector(), createAdministrator(), deactivate(), reactivate(), resetPassword(), listUsers(filter). |
| AuthenticateUserUseCase (in port) | login(phone, password): TokenPair; refresh(token): TokenPair. |
| UserRepositoryPort (out port) | save(User), findByPhoneNumber(...), findById(...), findAll(filter, pageable). |
| PasswordHasherPort / TokenIssuerPort (out ports) | Abstract the hashing algorithm and JWT mechanics away from the domain. |

**domain.submission**

| **Class(es)** | **Responsibility** |
|---------------|-------------------|
| Submission | Aggregate root. Factory Submission.record(respondent, response, provenance); enforces one-response-per-formtype and delegates uniqueness check to RespondentUniquenessPolicy before allowing status PENDING/SYNCED. |
| Respondent, BypResponse, IypResponse, LgoResponse, ParishMonitoringResponse | Child entities of Submission; each *Response validates its own form-specific field/conditional rules via ConditionalFieldValidator. |
| RespondentUniquenessPolicy | Domain service: isUnique(phone, formType, period) — used identically on client (against local cache) and server (against SubmissionRepositoryPort). |
| ConditionalFieldValidator | Domain service: validates FORM-08/09/10/12 rules (mandatory fields, show/hide logic, age >= 15, min text length) per form type. |
| SubmitSurveyUseCase (in port) | submit(SubmissionCommand): SubmissionResult — used both by the online submit flow and by SyncQueuedSubmissionsUseCase replay. |
| SyncQueuedSubmissionsUseCase (in port) | syncBatch(List<SubmissionCommand>): List<SyncResult> — idempotent via deviceSubmissionId. |
| CheckRespondentUniquenessUseCase (in port) | check(phone, formType, period): boolean — used for the pre-submit warning (UNIQ-02). |
| GetCollectorSubmissionCountUseCase (in port) | countToday(collectorId): int (FORM-13). |
| SubmissionRepositoryPort (out port) | save, findById, existsByPhoneFormTypeAndPeriod, findByFilters(criteria, pageable). |

**domain.location**

| **Class(es)** | **Responsibility** |
|---------------|-------------------|
| District, SubCounty, Parish, Village | Small reference-data aggregates. |
| QueryLocationHierarchyUseCase (in port) | listDistricts(), listSubCounties(districtId), listParishes(subCountyId), listVillages(parishId), fullBundle() (for offline pre-load, SYNC-05). |
| LocationRepositoryPort (out port) | Read-only queries against the four reference tables. |

**domain.dashboard**

| **Class(es)** | **Responsibility** |
|---------------|-------------------|
| SubmissionSummary, DistrictAggregate, DataCollectorLeaderboardEntry, TimeSeriesPoint, PendingSyncSnapshot | Read models (DTO-like, no identity/behaviour) returned by dashboard queries. |
| PublicAnonymisedRecord | Read model guaranteed free of PII, used only by public-facing queries/exports. |
| QueryAdminDashboardUseCase (in port) | summary(filter), chart(type, filter), collectorTracker(filter), pendingSyncQueue(). |
| QueryPublicDashboardUseCase (in port) | summary(filter), chart(type, filter), heatmap(filter) — always routes through AnonymisationProjector. |
| ExportDatasetUseCase (in port) | exportCsv(filter), exportExcel(filter), exportPdfReport(filter). |
| DashboardReadPort / ExportGeneratorPort (out ports) | Abstract the aggregate SQL/JPQL queries and the file-generation mechanics. |

**application.***

| **Class(es)** | **Responsibility** |
|---------------|-------------------|
| UserManagementService, AuthenticationService | Implement domain.user in-ports; orchestrate repository + password/token out-ports; publish domain events. |
| SubmitSurveyService, SyncService, UniquenessCheckService, CollectorSelfServiceService | Implement domain.submission in-ports; SyncService additionally writes sync_audit_log entries and applies exponential-back-off status bookkeeping consumed by the client (SYNC-04). |
| LocationQueryService | Implements domain.location in-ports; thin pass-through with caching. |
