| **Class(es)** | **Responsibility** |
|---------------|-------------------|
| *Controller classes | Thin — deserialize request → map to command/query via *Mapper → invoke the relevant in-port (use case) → map result to *Response DTO. No business logic lives here. |
| dto package | Immutable Java records per request/response payload (see REST API section). |
| mapper package | MapStruct mappers between REST DTOs and domain model/commands. |
| GlobalExceptionHandler | Translates domain exceptions (e.g. DuplicateRespondentException, UnderageRespondentException, InactiveAccountException) into RFC 7807 problem+json with correct HTTP status. |

