| *RepositoryAdapter classes | Implement the domain out-ports; translate between JPA entities and domain aggregates/value objects. |
| DashboardReadRepositoryAdapter | Implements DashboardReadPort using native/JPQL aggregate queries (GROUP BY district/form_type/gender/etc.) against submissions + response tables; kept separate from the write-side repositories to preserve CQRS separation. |

