# 4. REST API Specification

*All endpoints are versioned under /api/v1. Authenticated endpoints require a Bearer JWT access token issued by /api/v1/auth/login. Admin-only endpoints additionally enforce role = ADMIN via Spring Security method security; Data-Collector-only endpoints enforce role = DATA_COLLECTOR. Public endpoints require no Authorization header and never return PII fields (enforced by AnonymisationProjector, see Section 1, Reporting & Analytics context). List endpoints support standard page/size/sort query parameters unless noted otherwise.*

